---
// About Us section
---

<section id="about" class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Image side -->
      <div class="relative animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/images/portfolio/summit-view-truck.jpg"
            alt="Summit View Landscape branded work truck"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="800"
            height="600"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Floating stat card -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 rounded-xl bg-brand-blue p-6 text-white shadow-xl sm:-bottom-8 sm:-right-8">
          <p class="font-heading text-h2 font-extrabold leading-none">100+</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white/80">Projects Completed</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text side -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="--delay: 150ms">
        <p class="font-heading text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue">
          About Summit View
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-heading text-h2 font-extrabold text-brand-black sm:text-h1">
          Your Neighbors, Your Landscapers
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Summit View Landscape is a locally owned and operated landscaping company
          right here in Idaho. We started with a simple mission: deliver honest,
          high-quality outdoor services that make our neighbors proud of their properties.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-body leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Whether it's a full backyard transformation, seasonal clean-up, or ongoing lawn
          maintenance, we treat every yard like it's our own. Our crew takes pride in
          showing up on time, communicating clearly, and leaving your property better
          than we found it.
        </p>

        <!-- Value props -->
        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-5">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-blue pl-4">
            <p class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-black">Idaho Based</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Locally owned &amp; operated</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-blue pl-4">
            <p class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-black">Licensed &amp; Insured</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Fully covered for your peace of mind</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-blue pl-4">
            <p class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-black">Clear Communication</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">No surprises, just great service</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-blue pl-4">
            <p class="font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-black">5-Star Reviews</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Trusted by our community</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
